high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the toilet, turn left then walk towards the sink.
Pick up the spray bottle located on the right side of the sink closest to the wall.
Turn around then walk towards the shower, then head left towards the toilet.
Place the spray bottle on the right side on the back of the toilet.
Turn around then head towards the bath tub, then turn right heading for the sink.
Pick up the spray bottle on the sink.
Turn around then walk towards the shower, then head left towards the toilet.
Place the second spray bottle to the right of the first one, close to the wall.
anns.task_desc: Place two spray bottles side by side on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn left and head to the right sink.
Pick up the rightmost green spray bottle.
Turn around and walk around the toilet to the other side.
Place the spray bottle on the toilet tank.
Walk around the toilet and ahead to the left sink.
Pick up the green spray bottle.
Turn around and walk around the toilet to the other side again.
Place the spray bottle on the toilet tank to the right of the first one.
anns.task_desc: Place two spray bottles on a toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn and move to stand facing the sink that's closest to the wall with the toilet.
Pick up the green spray bottle that's to the right of the sink.
Turn around and move to stand between the toilet and shower, facing the toilet.
Place the spray bottle on the lid of the toilet's tank.
Move back to the vanity, but this time stand in front of the left sink.
Pick up the spray bottle from the counter between the two sinks.
Turn around and carry the bottle to stand between the toilet and shower, facing the toilet.
Place the spray bottle behind the other you previously left on the lid of the tank.
anns.task_desc: Move two green spray bottles to the lid of the toilet's tank.
